// changes may happen between Phase 1 and Phase 2. Once Phase 2 confirms the transport
// (subprocess/gRPC over stdio), the contract is frozen at v0.
//
// Compatibility rule: the host accepts a plugin when host.Major == plugin.Major AND
// host.Minor >= plugin.Minor. A plugin with a higher Minor than the host is rejected
// (host may be missing optional fields the plugin depends on). Minor bumps are additive
// (new optional fields only). Major bumps are breaking.
//
// # SARIF Mapping Intent
//
// Fields are chosen to lower cleanly into a SARIF 2.1 `result` + `codeFlows`:
//   - Finding.id        → result.ruleId
